OL,3,CJo Stevens no longer Welsh Secretary
OL,4,Cas Andy Burnham becomes PM
OL,6,FJo Stevens will no longer serve as
OL,7,FWelsh Secretary under Andy Burnham,
OL,8,Fshe has announced.
OL,10,FAndy Burnham became prime minister
OL,11,Fafter "kissing hands" with the King on
OL,12,FMonday ` the private ceremony by which
OL,13,Fhe accepted the invitation to form a
OL,14,Fgovernment.
OL,16,FHe immediately begun his Cabinet
OL,17,Freshuffle, with Rachel Reeves losing
OL,18,Fher job as Chancellor.
