OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784569707
OL,3,CJo Stevens no longer Welsh Secretary
OL,4,Cas Andy Burnham becomes PM
OL,6,FAmongst those losing their jobs was Jo
OL,7,FStevens MP, who has served as
OL,8,FSecretary of State for Wales under Sir
OL,9,FKeir Starmer.
OL,11,FPosting to X, she said carrying out
OL,12,Fthe role had been a "privilege and an
OL,13,Fhonour".
OL,15,FShe wrote: "As Welsh Secretary, my
OL,16,Fpriorities were always to drive public
OL,17,Fand private investment into Wales,
OL,18,Fcreate jobs and opportunities and put
OL,19,Freal power in the hands of Welsh
OL,20,Fcommunities.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
