PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784569707
OL,3,CJo Stevens no longer Welsh Secretary
OL,4,Cas Andy Burnham becomes PM
OL,6,F"Wales has seen the biggest budget
OL,7,Fsettlement for our public services in
OL,8,Fthe history of devolution, our steel
OL,9,Findustry saved and transformed for the
OL,10,Ffuture, the largest public investment
OL,11,Fin Wales in history through new
OL,12,Fnuclear at Wylfa, a generational
OL,13,Fcommitment of #14bn for our Welsh
OL,14,Frailways, the best local growth fun
OL,15,Fsettlement of any of the UK nations
OL,16,Fand so much more."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
