OL,3,CJo Stevens no longer Welsh Secretary
OL,4,Cas Andy Burnham becomes PM
OL,6,FAndy Burnham has promised to deliver
OL,7,Fthe biggest change to British politics
OL,8,Fin 40 years as he became Prime
OL,9,FMinister and swept away key figures
OL,10,Ffrom Sir Keir Starmer's government.
OL,12,FHe promised to provide early
OL,13,F"breathing space" for households
OL,14,Fstruggling with the cost of living,
OL,15,Fvowed to end rough sleeping and set
OL,16,Fout a goal of "reindustrialising
OL,17,FBritain".
