OL,3,CJo Stevens no longer Welsh Secretary
OL,4,Cas Andy Burnham becomes PM
OL,6,FSpeaking outside the door to No 10 Mr
OL,7,FBurnham said he would deliver "a new
OL,8,Fpolitical model and a new economic
OL,9,Fmodel" for Britain.
